Step 1: Register the Nexus NuGet proxy as a PSRepository
powershellRegister-PSRepository -Name "NexusPS" `
    -SourceLocation "https://nexus.bmwgroup.net/service/rest/repository/browse/nuget_proxy/" `
    -InstallationPolicy Trusted
If that doesn't work, try the NuGet v2 API endpoint format:
powershellRegister-PSRepository -Name "NexusPS" `
    -SourceLocation "https://nexus.bmwgroup.net/repository/nuget_proxy/" `
    -InstallationPolicy Trusted
Step 2: Search if Az.Accounts is available
powershellFind-Module -Name Az.Accounts -Repository NexusPS
Step 3: Install
powershellInstall-Module -Name Az.Accounts -Repository NexusPS -Force -AllowClobber -Scope AllUs
